        <li><strong>Easy to digest:</strong> Whey protein isolate absorbs quickly</li>
        <li><strong>Low sugar:</strong> Won't cause dumping syndrome</li>
        <li><strong>Smooth texture:</strong> No chunks or lumps to stress stomach</li>
        <li><strong>Budget-friendly:</strong> Under $3 per serving</li>
      </ul>
